An '''acidthrower''' was a weapon that sprayed out an [[Acid/Legends|acid]] capable of burning through anything it touched. Acid throwers were used by the [[Drovian]]s of [[Nim Drovis]] to repel the [[carnivorous mold]] that grew there. They had a range of twenty [[Foot/Legends|feet]].<ref name="POT">''[[Planet of Twilight]]''</ref>

